OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FIt was an historic county which looked
OL,7,Fset to miss out almost entirely on
OL,8,Flocal elections this year.
OL,10,FBut soon after ministers abandoned
OL,11,Fplans to postpone polling day, Sussex
OL,12,Fswiftly shaped up to be a key
OL,13,Felectoral battleground.
OL,15,FThe area is being seen as emblematic
OL,16,Fof the emerging five party system,
OL,17,Fwith Labour, the Conservatives,
OL,18,FLiberal Democrats, Green Party and
OL,19,FReform UK all hopeful of success in
OL,20,Fdifferent council contests.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
