FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FIn a new multi-party system, the most
OL,7,Fpolarising contests in Sussex appear
OL,8,Fto be for smaller borough and district
OL,9,Fauthorities along the South Coast.
OL,11,FLabour cabinet ministers have been
OL,12,Fcampaigning hard in Adur and Worthing
OL,13,Fover recent weeks.
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,16,Fsaid her party was "fighting for every
OL,17,Fvote in these local elections", on a
OL,18,Fvisit to Shoreham-by-Sea last week.
OL,26,@xD@TOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
