CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FWorthing Borough Council has been run
OL,7,Fby Labour since 2022, with
OL,8,Fneighbouring Adur District Council.
OL,10,FDespite not all seats being up for
OL,11,Felection this May, it is
OL,12,Fmathematically possible that Labour
OL,13,Fcould lose control of both councils.
OL,15,FPothole repairs, town centre
OL,16,Fredevelopment and better end-of-life
OL,17,Fcare were among the issues getting
OL,18,Fplayers at Marine Gardens Bowling Club
OL,19,Fexercised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
