OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FIn Worthing town centre, disruption
OL,7,Fcaused by the installation of a heat
OL,8,Fpump network and the closure of a
OL,9,Fseafront multi-story car park has
OL,10,Fimpacted trade at a local pottery cafe.
OL,12,FArt-ful has recently moved to new,
OL,13,Flarger premises but owner, Nina Reid,
OL,14,Fadmits they struggle to make a profit.
OL,16,F"The high street is just a nightmare"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
