FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,F"There's loads of businesses closing.
OL,7,FI don't know if it's because footfall
OL,8,Fhas gone down so much but parking is a
OL,9,Freally bad issue."
OL,11,FNational issues are also dominating
OL,12,Fdiscussion ahead of polling day at
OL,13,FWorthing Sailing Club. Instructor Andy
OL,14,FMonk tells me that water quality is an
OL,15,Foverriding issue for many people
OL,16,Fliving locally.
OL,18,F"We'd love the water quality to be
OL,19,Falways safe. We're a seaside town and
OL,20,Fspending time by the sea seems to
OL,21,Fboost people's health and wellbeing."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
