OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FIt is a sentiment shared by some of
OL,7,Fthe participants at a popular
OL,8,FBrazilian jiu-jitsu class taking place
OL,9,Fat the nearby Aragona Martial Arts
OL,10,FAcademy.
OL,12,FCoach James Lidbetter said:
OL,13,F"Constantly dumping waste in the ocean
OL,14,Fis a massive issue for us, because
OL,15,Fit's such a core part of where we
OL,16,Flive."
OL,18,FOn land, traffic disruption caused by
OL,19,Froadworks on the nearby A259 is
OL,20,Fgetting "ridiculous", according to
OL,21,Fclub owner Joanna Goodman.
OL,26,@xD@FO]|D@IOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
