FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FChief instructor Savio Aragona has
OL,7,Fnoticed an increased demand for
OL,8,Fmartial arts classes because of fears
OL,9,Fabout personal safety.
OL,11,F"There's a lot of people coming to us,
OL,12,Fthinking if everything is not going
OL,13,Fthe right way, I need to be able to
OL,14,Fhold myself and be aware of the basics
OL,15,Fof self defence."
OL,17,FBoth East and West Sussex County
OL,18,FCouncils have all their seats up for
OL,19,Felection for the first time since 2021.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
