FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FThe Conservatives currently run both
OL,7,Fcouncils, with an outright majority in
OL,8,FWest Sussex and a minority
OL,9,Fadministration in East Sussex.
OL,11,FThe Liberal Democrats hope to build on
OL,12,Ftheir success of unseating Tory MPs in
OL,13,F2024 in seats such as Chichester,
OL,14,FLewes and Eastbourne.
OL,16,FThe Lib Dems have ambitions of
OL,17,Fbecoming the largest party on both
OL,18,Fcounty councils in Sussex, according
OL,19,Fto a senior party source.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FBut the Lib Dems ` like Labour and the
OL,7,FConservatives ` are under no illusion
OL,8,Fof the renewed popularity of the
OL,9,FGreens and Reform UK.
OL,11,FParty leaders Zack Polanski and Nigel
OL,12,FFarage have both made campaign visits
OL,13,Fto East Sussex over recent weeks, in
OL,14,Fwhich they talked up their parties'
OL,15,Fchances of gaining seats on 7 May.
OL,17,FHastings ` famous for its battle of
OL,18,F1066 ` is now facing a unique
OL,19,Fpolitical contest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
