OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1776985387
OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FThe local authority currently has no
OL,7,Foverall control, with a Green minority
OL,8,Fadministration.
OL,10,FThe five parties leading the national
OL,11,Fopinion polls are joined in Hastings
OL,12,Fby independents standing under the
OL,13,Fbanner of the Jeremy Corbyn-backed
OL,14,FYour Party.
OL,16,FIndependent candidates will be
OL,17,Fstanding in seats across the region,
OL,18,Fwith national opinion polls not always
OL,19,Freflecting local concerns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
