OL,3,CSeaside showdown as five parties vie
OL,4,Cfor votes along the Sussex coast
OL,6,FA full list of the candidates stating
OL,7,Fin the above mentioned areas is
OL,8,Favailable on the council websites for
OL,9,FEast Sussex, West Sussex, Hastings,
OL,10,FCrawley, Adur and Worthing.
OL,12,FPolls are open from 7am till 10pm on
OL,13,FThursday, 7 May.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
